   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.60" region="speaker">Once you are logged into the system, creating an</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.60" end="00:00:06.20" region="speaker">eMod is simple.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.20" end="00:00:08.66" region="speaker">First select the contract from the dropdown menu in</p>
         <p begin="00:00:08.66" end="00:00:10.90" region="speaker">the New Modifications section.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.90" end="00:00:12.50" region="speaker">Once you have the appropriate contract</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.50" end="00:00:15.60" region="speaker">selected click &quot;Submit Contract&quot; and you are on</p>
         <p begin="00:00:15.60" end="00:00:17.60" region="speaker">your way.</p>
